{"tid":2462170,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"祖記得5個非賣品　C朗2500萬歐元賣得","createTime":"2021-03-26T00:07:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T00:51:40.000Z","uid":147522,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"58d8ec0dc50140819b1601aed9c5116a7647b00e","tid":2462170,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:07:58.000Z","msg":"意甲勁旅祖雲達斯今季成績令人失望，計劃今夏進行大換血，《米蘭體育報》指祖記只有5位球員屬於非賣品，但唔包括C朗，會方更加有意賤賣呢位葡萄牙巨星，只要有球會出到2,500萬歐元轉會費，就可以帶走C朗。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，祖記5位非賣品球員，包括費達歷高基艾沙、古路施夫斯基、艾法美路、馬菲斯迪歷特、丹尼路雷斯，其餘球員只要價錢合適都賣得，包括C朗，最令人驚訝係祖記只要求2,500萬歐元轉會費，相信係由於呢位射手已經36歲，無法要求高價出售。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，C朗年薪高達3,000萬歐元，即使低價放走佢，已經可以大大減輕球會財政負擔。<br />\n當今球壇有財力支付C朗天價人工嘅球會，實在唔多，有傳皇馬打算邀請佢回巢，巴黎聖日耳門、曼聯亦可能係佢嘅選擇。"},{"pid":"95c32afc14f90aa21c50b0bed9dab1d9172da5f3","tid":2462170,"uid":99725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:16:08.000Z","msg":"2500萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9095de44ebf04c22a91e1f5acf2b13758a46f190","tid":2462170,"uid":310469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:18:05.000Z","msg":"Danlio<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84362e7ca17152e3848ad53bc62772c70a420bfe","tid":2462170,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T00:19:15.000Z","msg":"2500萬 錫紙聯都買得起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9a219d873997374fa938832d2a8e6f9a38e0e1","tid":2462170,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84362e7ca17152e3848ad53bc62772c70a420bfe","tid"